data.title: Christina Milian Turned Up: Season 2
data.meta_description: This reality series follows the family life of Grammy-nominated singer Christina Milian. Her mom and sisters help to raise her young daughter as she tries to reinvigorate her career on a new label. Mom Carmen is her manager and business partner, but the time they spend together often stresses sisters Danielle and Lizzy. Danielle -- the voice of reason among the siblings -- has a newborn but a rocky beginning to her marriage. Lizzy -- a personal chef -- wants everyone to comprehend her lifestyle since her recent conversion to Orthodox Judaism.
